213 void setTopics()
214 {
215  rgb_image_mono = "/" + camera + "/" + rgb + "/" + RGB_IMAGE_MONO;
216  rgb_image_color = "/" + camera + "/" + rgb + "/" + RGB_IMAGE_COLOR;
217  rgb_image_rect_mono = "/" + camera + "/" + rgb + "/" + RGB_IMAGE_RECT_MONO;
218  rgb_image_rect_color = "/" + camera + "/" + rgb + "/" + RGB_IMAGE_RECT_COLOR;
219  depth_image_rect_raw = "/" + camera + "/" + depth + "/" + DEPTH_IMAGE_RECT_RAW;
220  depth_image_rect = "/" + camera + "/" + depth + "/" + DEPTH_IMAGE_RECT;
221  depth_image = "/" + camera + "/" + depth + "/" + DEPTH_IMAGE;
222  depth_points = "/" + camera + "/" + depth + "/" + DEPTH_POINTS;
223  ir_image_rect_ir = "/" + camera + "/" + ir + "/" + IR_IMAGE_RECT_IR;
224  depth_reg_sw_reg_image_rect_raw = "/" + camera + "/" + depth_registered + "/" + DEPTH_REG_SW_REG_IMAGE_RECT_RAW;
225  depth_reg_sw_reg_camera_info = "/" + camera + "/" + depth_registered + "/" + DEPTH_REG_SW_REG_CAMERA_INFO;
226  depth_reg_points = "/" + camera + "/" + depth_registered + "/" + DEPTH_REG_POINTS;

230 int main(int argc, char **argv) try
231 {
232  testing::InitGoogleTest(&argc, argv);
233  ros::init(argc, argv, "utest");
234 
235  ROS_INFO_STREAM("RealSense Camera - Starting rgbd_launch Tests...");

237  ros::NodeHandle nh;
238  getParams();

241  subscriber[0] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(rgb_image_mono, 1, topic0Callback, 0);
242  subscriber[1] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(rgb_image_color, 1, topic1Callback, 0);
243  subscriber[2] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(rgb_image_rect_mono, 1, topic2Callback, 0);
244  subscriber[3] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(rgb_image_rect_color, 1, topic3Callback, 0);
245  subscriber[4] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(depth_image_rect_raw, 1, topic4Callback, 0);
246  subscriber[5] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(depth_image_rect, 1, topic5Callback, 0);
247  subscriber[6] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(depth_image, 1, topic6Callback, 0);
248  subscriber[7] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::PointCloud2>(depth_points, 1, topic7Callback);
249  subscriber[8] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(ir_image_rect_ir, 1, topic8Callback, 0);
250  subscriber[9] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(depth_reg_sw_reg_image_rect_raw, 1, topic9Callback, 0);
251  subscriber[10] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::CameraInfo>(depth_reg_sw_reg_camera_info, 1, topic10Callback);
252  subscriber[11] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::PointCloud2>(depth_reg_points, 1, topic11Callback, 0);
253  subscriber[12] = nh.subscribe<sensor_msgs::Image>(depth_reg_sw_reg_image_rect, 1, topic12Callback, 0);
254 
255  ros::Duration duration;
